<div class="title">Alcoholism's a Bitch</div>
<div class="substance">Alcohol</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Jan&Exact=1">Jan</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Jan. "Alcoholism's a Bitch: An Experience with Alcohol (exp45224)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Dec 18, 2006. erowid.org/exp/45224</div>

